          <msContents>
            <summary><p>Written in a large gothic hand, 22 lines to a page. Initials and paragraphs marks in alternate red and blue, headings in red. Very large ornamental initial letter P in red and blue on first leaf and a smaller one (Q) on leaf 34v.</p>
<p>1. ff.1r-34r [i]Regimen Sanitatis,[/i] Arnoldus De Villanova</p>
<p>f.1r (red) Innomine domini amen Incipit regimen sanitatis ad in /clictum [sic] dominum regem aragonie, ab ordinatione huius libri/Magistro arnaldo de uilla noua directum. de man / sione aeris et congruitate eius. </p>
<p>  Rima pars uel conscideracio/sanitatis... f.34r line 10 ... et anno [sic] suauiter quan/tum poterit intromittatur. Et de hiis dicta sufficiant//deo gracias amen atque beate marie.// (red) Explicit breuis tractatus de regimine/sanitatis editus a magistro arnaldo de uil/la noua chatelano cuius anima requiescat in/pace. amen. </p>  
<p>2. ff.34v-39r [i]Regimen Sanitatis,[/i] Arnoldus De Villanova</p>
<p>f.34v (red) Incipit libellus regiminis sanitatis [sic] nobilium/Et eorum etiam Qui populariter seu uul/gariter se conregunt. edictus a magistro/aranldo de uilla nova cathalano./[Q]uia me rogastis ut uobis libe/llum conseruationis sanitatis scri/berem...f.39r...et mulitis in/firmitatibus elongetur, volente deo omnipotente/qui site per omnia secula seculorum benedictus. AMEN.//(red) Explicit.</p>
            </summary>
